summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lot 23, Block 5, Lake Dell Addition; Lots 7, 8 and 9, Block 13, B. F. Day's Eldorado Addition; with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-337 and 17-264 respectively.
